name: The Day I Accidentally Killed A Dreamer

metadata.name: Jocelyn, sing me a SAD song!
metadata.description:
" Rusted sunset,
muddy water,
tears,
the silence,
the last goodbye you said to your mother,
too late, 
when you give up on a dream
you kill a dreamer, not just a dream.. "


NEVE, 
2 Jul 2022

Edition: 1/1

4000 x 5823
